123
00:07:18,958 --> 00:07:20,250
[MILK MACHINE]
Moo...

124
00:07:20,333 --> 00:07:21,625
--[chattering]
--[ERUNA] Uhh...

125
00:07:21,708 --> 00:07:23,833
What was Enoyan thinking
just leaving this creepy guy

126
00:07:23,916 --> 00:07:26,458
at the door without taking
two seconds to come say hi?

127
00:07:26,541 --> 00:07:28,416
Very much his style,
though, ryui.

128
00:07:30,041 --> 00:07:32,666
It's weird that Seisa
hasn't swung by, yet, huh?

129
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:34,166
Now that you mention it,

130
00:07:34,250 --> 00:07:37,041
