about a ghost for a while, now.

146
00:08:06,416 --> 00:08:08,500
Correct, and all of us
at the newspaper club

147
00:08:08,583 --> 00:08:11,333
are ready to take down
this so-called ghost.

148
00:08:11,416 --> 00:08:12,416
Sounds cool.

149
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:13,833
