of this ghost.

153
00:08:19,875 --> 00:08:21,541
It's you, is it not?

154
00:08:21,625 --> 00:08:22,750
[ERUNA]
Huh?

155
00:08:22,833 --> 00:08:24,291
[RUMINA] Can you blame
me for accusing you

156
