that third member we needed.

164
00:08:40,875 --> 00:08:43,833
[RUMINA] And where is this
so-called third member?

165
00:08:43,916 --> 00:08:44,666
[ERUNA gasps]

166
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:46,333
Uh....

167
00:08:46,416 --> 00:08:47,875
Just admit it.

168
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:49,625
You guys are the ones behind
this ghost nonsense, aren't you?

169
00:08:49,708 --> 00:08:50,708
No, we're not!

170
00:08:50,791 --> 00:08:52,375
For real! It's not
them, so back off.

171
00:08:52,458 --> 00:08:55,375
Honestly, I don't know what this
ghost thing is about, either.

172
00:08:55,458 --> 00:08:56,666
